data.description: Welcome to Selwyn Park: Owner is a trailblazer with this updated 4 bedrooms/2.5 bathrooms including stylish kitchen with granite counters (Refrigerator stays). Half-bath and laundry conveniently located on first-level (washer/dryer stays). A first-level bedroom suite includes bathroom with blue-tooth access (lovely for your favorite music); large custom, walk-in closet for wardrobe, sitting area, and/or small office; and second closet for additional storage. You choose. The upper-level primary bedroom also features a walk-in closet with custom shelving. Two additional bedrooms and a bonus room great as office, TV room, or study.  Relax on your front porch or entertain on the deck in the rear yard. This home is packed with so many nice touches and conveniently located with close proximity to the Ivory/Baker Rec Center. Minutes from Camp North End, the North Carolina Music Factory and all the fun Uptown has to offer including entertainment, shopping, and sports.
